EN: She folded a paper airplane.

ZH: 请把这些文件叠好放在桌子上。
EN: Please fold these documents neatly and place them on the table.

ZH: 她把塑料袋叠得很整齐。
EN: She folded the plastic bags neatly.

ZH: 他打开地图叠了好几遍才找到正确的路线。
EN: He unfolded the map several times before finding the right route.

ZH: 他叠着双臂等候着我的指示。
EN: He folded his arms and waited for my instructions.

